He turns out to be the one who has a power to defeat of the Grand Evil, TaeRang sets on his way to find other weak creatures and their villages that are endangered by the unjust evil power. Considering that the zodiac horse is better than the roaring dog in all aspects, the Jade Emperor changed the zodiac horse to Pan Taoyuan. Since then, a series of wit and brave, funny stories have occurred in Pantaoyuan.
(translated from youku)

In order to protect themselves, the weak animals secretly selected four small animals as the special agent team after a long time. They are the strongest fighters-Forte, Semi, Lucy, Max! From then on they will shoulder the mission of defending Lanling Village and the small animals. They are different from ordinary little animals, each with different superpowers, to start thrilling fights with the evil party, and save those little animals in crisis. The strongest warriors wore cool armors and powerful weapons, dispatched agent cars and agent mechas for exciting battles, presenting a gorgeous visual beauty! Let us wait and see what wonderful performance the strongest fighter mini-agent team will do to defend Lanling Village! 
(translated from iqiyi)

The kind-hearted and simple rural old man Zhou Fugui went to the city with his son Tue Mao and his wife Shufen to live in a residential community in downtown Chongqing. The ordinary life of this family of three is the epitome and true portrayal of small families among Chongqing citizens. The sour, sweet, bitter, and spicy can be said to be full of flavors and vivid colors. The story shows the unique charm of New Chongqing and the new style of Chongqing people to the audience through laughter and curse, and vividly outlines a wonderful picture of urban and rural life. 
(translated from baidu baike)

title: Zhuang Zai Koudai Li De Baba

The reason why he gets smaller is because he is neither good at making money nor being an official, so he is often scolded by Yang Ge's mother. Every time his mother scolded him, his father's body shrank a little, and in the end he shrank to the size of his thumb. After getting smaller, his father's mind became very agile. He invented a series of things: cash cow, smart rice, dream maker, brainwashing gun, etc. These inventions brought earth-shaking changes to Yang Ge's family and the entire society. At the same time, terrorists also focused on his father's invention, and wanted to use his father's invention for evil. Can Yang Ge and his father defeat the terrorists and protect the earth? Peace and tranquility? (translated from iqiyi)

title: Tianmi Tegong Dui
synopsis: There is a parallel world underground in the Great Cloud Kingdom-Youlan Ancient Country, where the people here guard the nebula that maintains the balance of underground and above-ground resources for generations. One day, the nebula was broken into pieces and scattered to the earth. The king sent his two children, You Ming and Rainbow, to the earth world to find scattered nebula fragments, and the naughty sister, You You, also secretly followed his brothers to the ground. The three Yunbao brothers and sisters who were teleported to the Big Cloud World ran into Master Xuanwu who lived in the hot spring. Under the guidance of Master Xuanwu, the three brothers and sisters embarked on the path to find the debris, and the spirit of greed that had been following the three brothers and sisters waited for the opportunity to snatch Fragments. (translated from iqiyi)

Their daily life is to collect nectar hard, play to their heart's content, and struggle for their dreams, so in the small garden, they are constantly performing childlike and positive insect stories. Snow White and the dwarf were moved by her true feelings and perseverance, and decided to help her. The dwarves made a huge hot air balloon and took Snow White and the little girl to Bird Island. They only learned the true whereabouts of the missing father after seeing the divine bird after all the hardships. Snow White and the dwarf strayed into the trap and were caught on the way to save people. At this time, the queen appeared, wearing the most beautiful dress in the world, and the disappearance of father and the fate of the little girl are very important to this dress. Relationship. Where did the dress come from, how did everyone escape from danger, and can father and daughter finally be reunited?

One day, in the midst of a disturbance made by Taishou and his gang, Akko-chan accidentally broke the mirror. She made a grave and buried the broken pieces in the backyard. That night, Akko-chan was awakened by a flash of light and a kind voice which belongs to the Queen of the Mirror Kingdom. The Queen expresses her gratitude to Akko-chan for valuing the mirror so much and offers her a gift—a magical compact mirror. Whenever Akko-chan sings the magical words, she will transform into anything she wants.

title: Tian Tian Quan Baobei Zhi Feixing Leyuan

alternative_titles.ja: 甜甜圈宝贝之飞行乐园

synopsis:
The donut babies are a group of cute elves. They are innocent, kind, witty and brave, and can be transformed into various images and appear in a wonderful world. There are smart and active flying around, sweet and lovely Qiaomeimei, honest and honest peas, and sometimes mischievous, sometimes melancholy. In this series, they are a majestic little plane, working dutifully at the airport every day. The industrious small planes not only transport goods and protect the airport, but also deal with unexpected incidents that are caught off guard. They are busy every day. No matter what kind of problem, as long as the small planes unite and work together, they will eventually be solved.
(translated from youku)

title: Mini Tegong Dui X
synopsis:
In the vast universe, after a long period of time, four small animals were secretly selected to protect the peace of the earth as a "mini agent team". They are the strongest fighters: Fort, Semi, Lucy, Max ! Hundreds of years later, the threesome of the cosmic pirate Dandan group-Kara, Dante, and Danjo, discovered the sealed alien Jiesu on an asteroid, and released the seal to let him see again. Jesu’s power stems from the negative emotions (fear, sadness) emitted by the living body, which is called the energy of misfortune. This group of evil forces is planning to continuously create crises on the earth and obtain unfortunate energy from the life forms on the earth. In order to protect the earth, the mini-agent team has launched a fierce battle with evil forces! " 
(translated from iqiyi)

title: Xiao Feiji Ka Ka
synopsis: Kaka and his partners are a group of cute little planes, and they live happily in the scenic Rainbow Bay. They are warm, kind, hard-working, and full of love. Kaka is smart and lively, very responsible, and loves to behave; the smiling Uncle Lolo is a bit annoying recently, because he has reached the age of retirement; the young Mango Wen is naughty like a child who has not grown up; Is willing to serve everyone. Airplane babies love to show off exciting and startling flying stunts in the air, but they are usually very gentle and considerate, full of gentlemanly demeanor. They also get along well with the animals in Rainbow Bay. The film is relaxed and happy, showing the children the values of responsibility, cooperation, fraternity, tolerance and acceptance with the positive work and life attitude of the baby airplane. (translated from iqiyi)

title: Sai Ya Lixian Ji
synopsis:
It (animation) will let people all over the country and the world understand Qinghai Lake naked carp, a second-class national protected animal and a mysterious species unique to Qinghai. The person in charge of the Haibei State Party Committee emphasized that the simple and fresh beauty and warm and timeless love conveyed by the entire cartoon, and that humans should love nature and protect limited plant and animal resources. 
(translated from baidu baike)
